rows.label: qst103606_msg0001
rows.name:
Brionac... We thought we
had weakened them by defeating
their leaders, but...

rows.label: qst103606_msg0002
rows.name: It seems they're still going strong.

rows.label: qst103606_msg0003
rows.name:
It seems we have no choice but
to go to the Brionac Occupied
Zone and crush them thoroughly.

rows.label: qst103606_msg0004
rows.name:
You're right. We can't let those
who oppose the Empire run wild.
